        <updateDate>2017-03-23T13:53:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Addiction Recovery through Family Health Accounts Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to permit taxpayers to use tax-favored health reimbursement arrangements, health flexible spending arrangements, health savings accounts, and Archer medical savings accounts to pay for alcohol and drug addiction treatments for specified family members as if the expenses were incurred for a dependent. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
